title: Hiraman Khoskar
text: Hiraman Bhikabhai Khoskar is an Indian politician. He was elected as a Member of the <a href="Maharashtra%20Legislative%20Assembly">Maharashtra Legislative Assembly</a> for <a href="Igatpuri">Igatpuri</a> constituency. He received 31555 votes as belong to the <a href="Indian%20National%20Congress">Indian National Congress</a> party.
